subject: Tennis
United States Open (Tennis)
lead_paragraph: Roger Federer beat Marin Cilic on Saturday at the Open to win his 225th match at a major. On the women’s side, top-seeded Caroline Wozniacki rolled through a blustery afternoon to advance.
